	   <tr><td colspan=2>I will correct the illusions for you all....<br><br> Illusion: all races that have night vision will give you that<br><br> Illusion:Barbarian gives you the racial ability to slam<br> <br> Illusion:Troll gives you regen (1hp/tick)<br><br> Illusion:Earth Elemental strength buff with a max of 10 points<br><br> Illusion:Air Elemental gives you levitate<br><br> Illusion:Water Elemental gives enduring breath<br><br> Illusion:Fire Elemental gives you a Damage Shield with a max of 16<br><br> Illusion:Drybone gives a Fire resist buff max of 25<br><br> Illusion:Spirit Wolf increases ATK 15 & Cold Resist 10 <br><br> Illusion:Werewolf is a major melee buff<br><br><br>I hope this helps you, and like I always say Enchanters rule!!!!<br><br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;  Arynn<br>    Tier-Dal Enchanter of the 4th Circle<br>    Bristlebane server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
